Interface Moveable


  • public interface Moveable
    Interface to describe a moveable object. A moveable object can have a x-coordinate and a y-coordinate. The position and the individual coordinates can be set. The individual coordinates can be returned. The moveable object has a width and height that can be similarly set and returned. The moveable object has a speed that can also be set and returned.
